Text: Neither serial box or the new reader works. It says both may have been corrupted by a third party. Download at your peril, I'd suggest.
Yup, Serial Box 07-2010 is corrupt - does not instal into iSerial Reader. Will work with Serial Seeker though.
CORRECTION: Serial Box 07-2010 works, but only with the newest release of iSerial Reader 2.0.8, included in this torrent.
